&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Collect and analyze operations data to&amp;nbsp;identify&amp;nbsp;and implement&amp;nbsp;efficiency improvements for operational processes and workflows&amp;nbsp;and translate it into reporting, and recommendations for the development team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
