&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Developing and testing multi-agent autonomous systems and deploying in real-world environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Feature and algorithm development with an understanding of behavior trees&lt;/li&gt;
