&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Experience standing up automated hardware-in-the-loop testing infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Functional knowledge of software development, verification, and validation requirements for DO-178 and MIL-HDBK-516C&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Experience developing testable requirements and understanding of DO-178 and MIL-HDBK-516C verification objectives&lt;/li&gt;
