&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Verkada is transforming how organizations protect their people and places with an integrated, AI-powered platform. A leader in cloud physical security, Verkada helps organizations strengthen safety and efficiency through one connected software platform that includes solutions for video security, access control, air quality sensors, alarms, intercoms, and visitor management.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Over 30,000 organizations worldwide, including more than 100 companies in the Fortune 500, trust Verkada as their physical security layer for easier management, intelligent control, and scalable deployments. Founded in 2016, Verkada has expanded rapidly with 15 offices and 2,200+ full-time employees.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a high-bandwidth, craft-oriented Recruiter to partner with our Senior Design Recruiter and Design Hiring managers in scaling Verkada’s Product Design department from 30 to 46+ people. You will own the end-to-end lifecycle for specialized roles across UX Design, Industrial Design, and Packaging Design, ensuring we maintain an elite talent bar while expanding our footprint in the SF Bay Area and Taiwan.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the end-to-end recruitment process, from initial intake to offer negotiations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hunt for top design talent, including full-stack Product Designers, Design Systems experts, Packaging Design specialists and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shape and iterate our recruiting processes, working alongside Designers and Leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate Interviews for our UX and Industrial Design team, from screens to on-site interviews across global timezones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver a high touch, high-quality transparent, and honest candidate experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a brand ambassador for Verkada’s design team, ensuring every candidate—regardless of the outcome—has a world-class experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of full-cycle recruiting experience, preferably with a focus on Product Design, Software Engineering, Hardware Engineering, or Creative Agencies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced in high-volume sourcing environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to navigate and flourish in a fast-paced, start-up environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing multiple internal competing priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to excellence and top performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Local to the Bay Area - HQ in San Mateo, CA (or open to relocation)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to &quot;speak design&quot; and decipher what makes a polished design portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Staffing Agency or Startup Recruiting experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
