&lt;p data-start=&quot;2057&quot; data-end=&quot;2179&quot;&gt;Design, build, test, and deploy scalable backend services and systems with a strong emphasis on long-term maintainability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2180&quot; data-end=&quot;2295&quot;&gt;
