&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Debug and iterate rapidly across research and production ML stacks&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contribute to research culture through technical discussions and collaborative problem-solving&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
